data.description: Peaceful in a park-like setting. Custom built, 3bd/2ba home located on over one acre just north of Shelton. Open concept w/vaulted ceilings. Beautiful windows & dormers for lots of light. Large spacious kitchen w/plenty of workspace & storage. Home is a split bedroom design w/ master on one end & additional bedrooms located on the opposite. Master suite w/5 piece bath including jetted tub & oversized walk-in closet. French doors lead to a rear deck under the evergreen canopy. Fenced back yard w/small storage shed too! Large laundry room/mud room located off of the attached oversize 2 car garage. Nicely finished storage area. *New carpet throughout.* Located in the desirable Brockdale Community. Just minutes to Hwy 101 for an easy commute.
